snippet.title: Dark Alliance – Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Your Party. Their Funeral. Preorder Now – DarkAlliance.com. Battle legendary monsters with your friends in an explosive co-op action brawler set in the world of Dungeons & Dragons.
 
Available Everywhere June 22

Music: Ozzy Osbourne - Straight to Hell - https://ozzy.lnk.to/StraightToHell
